com.ae2dms.bubblebobble.model.removable.hostile.Monster
public class Monster extends Enemy
Monster inherits from Enemy. Monsters show up in all levels. A monster is the common enemy with all the properties of enemy.

      public void drawOn​(javafx.scene.canvas.GraphicsContext graphicsContext)
      Draw the monster on the canvas. Different image for different direction. If the enemy is in bubbled, then bubble wraps the enemy.
      指定者:
      drawOn 在类中 GameObject
      参数:
      graphicsContext - GraphicsContext type, draw calls to a Canvas using a buffer.
